item.title: Tryouts 2023
item.description: Join the trail Tryouts are set! Fill out our form for the 2023 season. Two open tryouts: Sunday May 21st, 4-7pm at Franklin HS (preferred for local players) Monday June 5th, 6-9pm at QA Bowl Playfield After each tryout we’ll invite some players to team practices over the next two weeks before offering a number of spots on the team. If you were able to make our 4v4 tournament on April 30th thanks for coming.

item.title: Tryouts 2024
item.description: Future roommates Fill out our 2024 tryout form! Tryouts schedule: Open tryout #1 Sunday May 12th 1-4pm Georgetown Playfield Open tryout #2 Sunday May 19th 2-5pm Genesee Park Closed tryout #1 Thursday May 23rd 6-9pm Hiawatha Playfield Closed tryout #2 Thursday May 30th 7-10pm Delridge Playfield FAQ What if I can’t make it to the open tryouts because I’m traveling/in college/at nationals? Don’t worry! This happens every year. We have an option in our form for “I can’t make these dates” we’ll figure out an alternative.
